My team is considering a buddy auto that pushes our alliance members off the start line and scores a coral (guaranteeing the auto RP). We generally use choreo to generate our trajectories, but can it be used for so-called “push” paths that are designed to push another bot? I just have some concerns that it may ruin the path or something else and couldn’t find any discussion on it
